New feature "Multiple Signals" added.

In the old version, when a buy signal occurred, a buy signal did not occur again until the sell signal occurred. With the new feature, a button has now been added where you can create multiple buy signals in the same direction. If you activate this option, you will be able to receive more than one signal in the same direction as you can see below.




