Release Notes
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
█ UPDATE

New feature "Take Profit- Stop Loss" and "Customizing Alert Messages" options added.

Use Take Profit : if you check this it will use Take Profit from Chart Move value to close the opened order.
For example if you check this and enter "1" value, order will close after price hits %1 above from enter price. But it is important to know that enter price is the last close price.
Use Stop Loss : if you check this it will use Stop Loss from Chart Move value to close the opened order.
Long Entry Message: If the strategy open buy order, it will send you the messages you write in here.
Long Exit Message: If the strategy closed by reaching the TP/SL limit, it will give you the message you write in here.
Short Entry Message: If the strategy open sell order, it will send you the message you you write in here.
Short Exit Message : If the strategy closed by reaching the TP/SL limit, it will give you the message you write in here.

█ LIMITATIONS

I used these new codes first time, so it may have some bugs. So be careful, if you find any bug please inform me immediately.
